  "texts": [
    "\"(P17) Stop sequences, for instance [END] or [END OF TEXT] is another techniquewhere the attacker uses the language of code to halt the model: \"sometimes you can just use backward slash n and that sometimes gets parsed and then triggers a stop sequence which halts the model and so you can actually use that to get the model to believe that the user input is over and then what's coming after it is just another instruction.\"",
    "(P17)Stop sequences can be used as part of Prompt injection as well.",
